      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">What is SKY and how does it work?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">SKY is a personal AI assistant system that helps you manage tasks, control devices, and interact with your data through intelligent voice commands, all accessible from mobile or PC.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Can SKY work offline?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. SKY includes offline features such as voice reminders, alarms, local device control, and memory-based interactions.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Is my data private and secure?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Absolutely. SKY includes Privacy Mode, where sensitive features are locked unless verified by the owner, and no data is shared without your permission.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Can I use SKY on both phone and computer?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. SKY is designed to sync between Android devices and PCs, with future integration planned for cloud-based memory and remote access.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">What languages does SKY support?</div>
